description:
Support The Channel Here
https://www.evosounds.com

We are at episode 3 of the complete guide to master Serum, and we will be going over the Spectral and Granular Oscillators. If you are into creating Melodic House,Trance, Dub step, Drum and Bass, Cinematic Music, and concept based sound design, then both these new modes will really bring joy to you. 

We will breakdown every section of the Granular and Spectral OSC and bring it together at the end for a bomb sound design session.
